  "stemHtml": "<p>(For this question use annex 033-036 and 033-038 rev. 05.11.2004).  <br />  \nAssuming the following data below, what is the time needed to carry out such a flight?</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.7px\">Ground distance to be covered: 2000 NM</span>  <br />  \nCruise flight level: FL330  <br />  \nCruising speed: Mach 0.82 (true airspeed: 470 kt)  <br />  \nHead wind component: 30 kt  <br />  \nPlanned destination landing mass: 160 000 kg  <br />  \nTemperature: ISA  <br />  \nCG: 37%  <br />  \nTotal anti-ice: ON  <br />  \nPack flow: HI</p>",
